Flex						                                        Grid
flex is one directional				                          grid is two directional
flex is flexible and easy to work		                    complex but very useful
in flex we have only limited tools		                  in grid we have advanced tools
flex is bydefault a responsive webpage		              we can make grid responsive using some tools


display:grid; -- it defines the grid container
grid-template-rows -- it specifies how many rows it contains and how much space each row occupies
grid-template-columns -- it specifies how many columns it contains and how much space each columns occupies
grid-row -- it specifies the start and end of particular row
grid column -- it specifies the start and end of particular column
